{"tid":1011214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民願望太沉重？　林村仿真許願樹折枝","createTime":"2019-02-06T15:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T12:51:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"70133e268c515424e197f85ba2c3ca99fe6b54b5","tid":1011214,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/photo/bkn-20190206195330411-0206_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190206222348\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190206195330411-0206_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190206222348&h=69d4fd2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少市民趁新春到大埔林村行大運，有網民今日(6日)於社交群組上傳一段影片，林村的仿真許願樹疑「頂唔住」海量祈福寶牒，有樹枝折斷塌下，需由數名男子將「斷枝」搬離。<br />\n<br />\n網民於傍晚6時在Facebook「Tai Po 大埔」群組上傳影片，幾名男子及保安將掛滿祈福寶牒的膠製「斷枝」搬離場。網民紛紛留言：「好難唔冧，頂到咁耐算係咁」、「不如唔好再搞啦」及「睇嚟要升級到金屬樹幹先得」。<br />\n<br />\n協辦單位負責人潘小文解釋，許願樹非因不勝負荷而倒塌，是有一名男子嫌寶牒拋得不夠高，跳高擬把寶牒取回時不慎將樹枝一併拉斷，工作人員已即時將斷枝處理好，大會亦無意追究。<br />\n<br />\n潘指明日(7日)將用鐵欄圍封起許願樹，使市民不能靠近樹枝，若寶牒拋至鐵欄內也不得取回，不過為增加遊人拋中的機會，明日起寶牒買一送一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/bkn-20190206195330411-0206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190206%2Fbkn-20190206195330411-0206_00822_001.html&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=209e63ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/bkn-20190206195330411-0206_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5273c02505ce596b0c4f10c58ee277113a4352a5","tid":1011214,"uid":69886,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"凶兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196992332f489fce372ee8607f8a663624637490","tid":1011214,"uid":194298,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"牛又死，樹又冧，仲有小人幫你抽中下簽<br />\n<br />\n香港人今年自己睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769080cadd2fe253a64cccf645cbb243c75b155c","tid":1011214,"uid":205462,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>許願樹非因不勝負荷而倒塌，是有一名男子嫌寶牒拋得不夠高</strong><br />\n只有某國家嘅人，先會咁欠缺公民教育同唔知足啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a4bd01626f7f5616af81bcf43c28f177122491","tid":1011214,"uid":53026,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2005年真許願樹倒冧，董建華下台.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets